title: Hour 3 - College Football, Donovan  Mitchell to Cavaliers
itunes:title: Hour 3 - College Football, Donovan  Mitchell to Cavaliers
description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, it's reaction time to a number of exciting college football games from Thursday night. Dan and company also reflect on guard Donovan Mitchell's trade to the Cleveland Cavaliers and possible reasons for Tampa Bay quarterback Tom Brady's absence from training camp.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
